rComments: Although he's monotone, his lectures are great and well organized and the tests reflect what he does in class/tutorials/assignments

Prof. Aoude's way of teaching and delivering the course is just excellent and he's giving very useful feedback after every assignment/exam. Even though this course has a more than average workload, every component of the course really helps to learn. Exams are really similar to the practice questions so practice with those and you should be fine.
teacherRatingTags: ['Lots of homework', 'Gives good feedback', 'Accessible outside class']

rComments: Really good prof, lectures are super clear and straightforward. He explains really well and his course is amazingly organized. Lots of homework, quiz and videos to watch but they are really helpful to understand the content

This prof really cares about his students' success. He's flexible when it comes to grading and he's a very straight forward guy when he teaches. He relies on a bit of online learning, which is quite organized. There's easy online quizzes and the homework is easy. Exams are very similar to the homework. And there's also a bridge building project.

This prof is really nice and sweet, he'll give you chances for homework or exams if ever you encounter issues. His videos for the hybrid class are dry and his teaching is a bit dry, but the course being so straightforward and easy makes it tolerable.
Great prof, would definitely take again

Hassan is straight to the point. Go to class, do the examples, and watch his online tutorials & you will pass with flying colours. Very helpful and responds to emails right away. Exam material is identical to questions solved in assignments, class, and tutorials. No theory in exams just problem solving. Great notes and well organized. Overall A+
CVG2540, Hybrid class. Very straightforward midterm and exam. Clear expectations. Attend class and do the assignments and you will have no trouble getting a high grade.
Great prof! Material can be tough, but gives many examples and allows a 2-sided cheat sheet for the exams.
gives you a lot of examples that help you understand how to do the topic
